org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.textsem

Class IdentifiedAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • Annotation
      • org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.textsem.IdentifiedAnnotation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContextAnnotation, DateAnnotation, EntityMention, EventMention, FractionAnnotation, Markable, MeasurementAnnotation, Modifier, NonSmokerNamedEntityAnnotation, PersonTitleAnnotation, RangeAnnotation, RomanNumeralAnnotation, SmokerNamedEntityAnnotation, TimeAnnotation, TimeMention, UnknownSmokerNamedEntityAnnotation

    public class IdentifiedAnnotation
extends Annotation
    Any span of text that has been discovered or flagged for some reason, such as a Named Entity. Allows for mapping to an ontology. Generalized from cTAKES: org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.IdentifiedAnnotation. Updated by JCasGen Wed Sep 30 11:06:15 EDT 2015 XML source: /Users/pei/workspace/apache-ctakes/3.2.2/ctakes-ytex-uima/target/jcasgen/typesystem.xml
